Accordingly, we do not accept or assume any liability or any duty of care for any other purpose or to any other person to whom this certificate is shown or into whose hands it may come without our prior consent in writing.We have not audited books of accounts of the entity , the certificate is prepared basis the data provided to us.As a conservative approach we have shown total booking received amount as amount withdrawn from RERA Account. As informed to us by the promoter there was no unused material lying in stock as on the date of certification. Additional incidential cost is taken for certifying cost incurred and paid.
